{"word":"G850 - αὐχμηρός - auchmērós - owkh-may-ros' - Dark","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">αὐχμηρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">auchmērós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">owkh-may-ros'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Dark</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"இருளுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"squalid, dirty"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03B1;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03C7;&#x03BC;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C2;</b> <b>auchmos</b> (probably from a base akin to that of <a href=\"#/G109 - ἀήρ - aḗr - ah-ayr'/109\">G109</a>; <i>dust</i>, as <i>dried</i> by wind); properly <i>dirty</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>obscure:</i> - dark.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}